*******************************************
** CPSComment V0.3.1 [R1 build 2006/03/30-02:16 by anahide]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPSComment/trunk Revision: 34814
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Added Spanish translation.
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Modifying a comment indexed it with a wrong path in catalog.
- Comments are not indexed anymore.
- The ModifyPortalContent permission, required for datamodel commit, was
  missing on comments.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Installer does not use CPSInstaller anymore, it calls the setup tool and
  imports the CPSRelation and CPSComment extension profile.


*******************************************
** CPSComment V0.3.0 [R1 build 2006/03/08-15:49 by anahide]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPSComment/trunk Revision: 34174
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Added possibility to delete a comment.
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Comments were deleted when re-publishing a commented document.
- Do not raise an error when deleting a comment that is not found.
- Comment icon was missing.
- Comment identifiers are chosen among free repository docids so that there is
  no collision between proxies and comments unique identifiers.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- API changes.
- Be able to specify an id when creating a comment ; useful for tests.

