*******************************************
** CPSComment V0.2.1 [R1 build 2006/02/24-13:45 by anahide]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPSComment/trunk Revision: 33454
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Portlet showing comments crashed on non-proxy objects like the portal.
- Extension profile did not set up translations.
- Useless actions have been removed.
- Comments and relations were not deleted when document was deleted
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Tool is now called portal_comment to avoid collision with portal_discussion.
- Comment portal type name has been changed into 'Comment' instead of
  'CPS Comment'.

